Enclosing class:
ConstructorCallVisitor 
     public class
     
      ConstructorCallVisitor.ReplaceNewInstructionCodeAdapter
extends org.objectweb.asm.CodeAdapter

Replaces 'new' instructions with a call to the compiled JoinPoint instance.
It does the following: - remove NEW when we know (from first visit) that it matchs - remove DUP that follows NEW - replace INVOKESPECIAL with call to JP

Author:
Alexandre Vasseur
